  "read_terms": "Read Terms",
  "read_privacy": "Read Privacy",
  "terms_acceptance_title": "1. Acceptance of Terms",
  "terms_acceptance_desc": "By accessing or using ZYNMART, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws. If you do not agree, you may not use the platform. ZYNMART reserves the right to update these terms at any time with notice to registered users.",
  "terms_account_title": "2. Account Responsibilities",
  "terms_account_desc": "You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your Pi Network account credentials. Any activity conducted through your account is your responsibility. ZYNMART is not liable for unauthorized access resulting from your failure to secure credentials.",
  "terms_conduct_title": "3. Prohibited Conduct",
  "terms_conduct_desc": "Users may not list counterfeit goods, engage in fraudulent transactions, manipulate product reviews, or circumvent ZYNMART commission systems. Violations result in immediate account suspension and may be reported to Pi Network authorities.",
  "terms_ip_title": "4. Intellectual Property",
  "terms_ip_desc": "All platform content, design, logos, and trademarks are the exclusive property of ZYNMART. Users retain ownership of their uploaded product images but grant ZYNMART a non-exclusive license to display and promote listed items.",
  "terms_dispute_title": "5. Dispute Resolution",
  "terms_dispute_desc": "All disputes between buyers and sellers are subject to ZYNMART's arbitration process. ZYNMART's decision on disputes involving platform commissions is final. Legal disputes must be filed in the jurisdiction of Tunisia.",
  "privacy_collect_title": "1. Information We Collect",
  "privacy_collect_desc": "ZYNMART collects your Pi Network username, transaction metadata, browsing behavior within the platform, product interaction data, and device identifiers. We do not collect financial credentials or private Pi wallet keys.",
  "privacy_use_title": "2. How We Use Your Information",
  "privacy_use_desc": "Collected data is used to personalize your experience, recommend products, process transactions, prevent fraud, and improve platform performance. We do not sell personal data to third parties.",
  "privacy_sharing_title": "3. Data Sharing",
  "privacy_sharing_desc": "We share data with Pi Network for authentication, with shipping partners for order fulfillment, and with analytics providers under strict data processing agreements. All partners are GDPR-compliant.",
  "privacy_rights_title": "4. Your Rights",
  "privacy_rights_desc": "You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. Submit requests via the Help center. ZYNMART will respond within 30 days. Residents of the EU and Tunisia have additional rights under GDPR and Tunisian Data Protection Law.",
  "privacy_retention_title": "5. Data Retention",
  "privacy_retention_desc": "Transaction records are retained for 7 years per legal requirements. Behavioral data is anonymized after 12 months. Account data is deleted within 90 days of account closure upon request.",
